an oi director of shorenstein aparc's stanford china program discusses stanford's expansion into china shorenstein aparc in the news the stanford daily on october 25 2007 stanford china program inaugural event october 19 2007 shorenstein aparc announcement support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 9632 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
